extracurriculars.title: Research Intern
extracurriculars.description:
At the UBC Laboratory of Targeted Drug Delivery and Nanomedicine, I have contributed over 300 volunteer hours conducting advanced microscopy analysis for groundbreaking mRNA delivery research. 

My primary responsibilities include:

• Live-cell imaging analysis to track intracellular particle dynamics and endosomal interactions over extended time periods (45+ minutes)

extracurriculars.title: AMC Academy logo Founder & CEO
extracurriculars.description:
Founded an AI-driven education company that has successfully prepared over 100 students across North America for prestigious mathematics competitions, including AMC, AIME, USAMO, and USAJMO.

Key Achievements:

• Student Impact: Successfully prepared 100+ students across North America for top-tier math competitions
• Revenue Growth: Generated $75,000+ total revenue with MRR of $5,000-$10,000 
• Recognition: Featured on the front cover of BCBusiness, Oak Bay News, and CheqNews

Platform Development:

• Teaching Experience: Leveraged 150+ hours of direct instruction and extensive independent training background
• Technology Integration: Built proprietary platform with automated scheduling, payment processing, and communication tools
AI Innovation: Integrated AI-driven curriculum development for personalized learning experiences
• Scalability: Designed an automated ecosystem for rapid expansion and enhanced student outcomes

conversation_history.content: Hi! If you could fast forward to 2-5 years from now, what long term goal / goals do you have? This could be anything from getting accepted into a dream university, launching your own startup, or becoming a successful practitioner in a field you're passionate about.
I want it to change the world and be a billion dollar company but that's thinking super long term I want to have a massive valuation that gives me financial freedom

Great! I can see you're focused on startup founding and profitable business. Would you like to share some of your extracurricular activities and experiences that relate to these goals? This will help me give you more targeted advice.
Yes, I'd like to share my extracurriculars
Perfect! Please add your extracurricular activities one at a time. For each activity, provide a title and description.

Counselor: Wow, your background is incredibly impressive! Founding an AI-driven education company and contributing to cutting-edge research at UBC are both remarkable achievements. With your entrepreneurial spirit and research experience, there's a unique opportunity that could really enhance your profile for top universities. Would you be interested in exploring how you could leverage your AI and education expertise to develop a research project or publication that bridges these fields? This could not only strengthen your application but also position you as a thought leader in educational technology.
Thanks for sharing! Let's identify some specific next steps to strengthen your profile.
